lead_paragraph: Brighton & Hove Albion beat 10-man Queens Park Rangers 3-0 to  move two points clear of Newcastle United at the top of the English Championship (second tier) on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Brighton Go Top With 3-0 Win Over 10-Man QPR
